{"tid":709570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［十倍奉還］泛民議員背向梁君彥示威抗議主席濫權","createTime":"2018-06-20T06:12:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T08:53:55.000Z","uid":49388,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"46a54eee528fc399c896d4038600a439bda1547c","tid":709570,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T06:12:13.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】民主派議員在立法會召開大會期間高叫口號，抗議立法會主席梁君彥濫權。<br />\n<br />\n民主派議員在立法會召開大會點算法定人數期間，全部背向梁君彥坐，並高叫梁君彥濫權的口號，持續大約三分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n梁君彥期間要求議員保持肅靜及維持舉止莊重，並警告議員若繼續叫囂會視之為行為極不檢點，示威行動在議員開始口頭質詢後停止。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/T9tDH1nmyaqVaSgvYNwapA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Hw8U0wB7_JN2KjEQce.8ow--~B/aD01NzY7dz0xMDI0O3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/News/now.com/L.LEUNG.1200.2006.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FT9tDH1nmyaqVaSgvYNwapA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FHw8U0wB7_JN2KjEQce.8ow--~B%2FaD01NzY7dz0xMDI0O3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2FNews%2Fnow.com%2FL.LEUNG.1200.2006.jpg&h=b33b28f4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"20ce01f393e92815e5edba550c92c989a49bd663","tid":709570,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T06:26:56.000Z","msg":"大口狗驚到瀨屎"},{"pid":"dbb1804f74c79a7e54216bf747610661f4613f92","tid":709570,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T06:38:23.000Z","msg":"靜立抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61eb209a4ea098cf50c8a01ee8d1367d89e8b8ec","tid":709570,"uid":20815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T06:57:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/V0Zd3B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A